author: rich
msg: Got rid of the majority of calls to getAttribute/setAttribute on the request, and replaced them with calls to methods on a request wrapper created early in the request process.  Aside from the swell hard-type getters/setters, this should boost performance, which is hurt by all the hashmap lookups.  It will take some testing under load to verify this.
